Shots have been fired.

00:13:11.530 --> 00:13:12.630
>> Downtown New Orleans became a

00:13:12.630 --> 00:13:14.330
looter's free-for-all.

00:13:14.330 --> 00:13:15.260
>> They represent a frightening

00:13:15.260 --> 00:13:17.660
breakdown of law and order.

00:13:17.660 --> 00:13:18.930
>> NARRATOR: But early media

