And from that came rumors and

00:14:14.030 --> 00:14:15.460
innuendo that unfortunately some

00:14:15.460 --> 00:14:17.930
officials repeated as fact.

00:14:17.930 --> 00:14:19.230
>> You getting ready to see

00:14:19.230 --> 00:14:19.960
something that I'm not sure

00:14:19.960 --> 00:14:21.500
you're ready to see.

00:14:21.500 --> 00:14:22.000
There are people standing out

00:14:22.000 --> 00:14:23.960
there.

