believing these things as well,

00:14:46.230 --> 00:14:47.760
initially.

00:14:47.760 --> 00:14:49.060
>> NARRATOR: On August 30,

00:14:49.060 --> 00:14:50.460
Deputy Chief Riley met with

00:14:50.460 --> 00:14:51.500
