>> Who said that?

00:16:20.430 --> 00:16:21.530
>> I didn't say that.

00:16:21.530 --> 00:16:22.230
I heard rumors that someone else

00:16:22.230 --> 00:16:23.060
said that.

00:16:23.060 --> 00:16:24.230
